Subject: [PATCH 08/14] dt-bindings: arm: amlogic: add support for the
 ODROID-N2+

HardKernel ODROID-N2+ uses a revised Amlogic S922X v2 chip that supports
higher cpu clock speeds than the original ODROID-N2.

